      ],
      "text": "The wolf spirit is a ferocious beast and servant to the Mother of Faces. He serves his master by choosing the paths for her seasonal travels through Forgetful Valley."
    },
    {
      "body": "Around 83 ${link_0}, the wolf spirit was spotted while drinking from a stream by ${link_1}, who had turned to a life of isolation in the forest near a river.",
