      "section": [
        "Wolf spirit",
        "History"
      ],
      "text": "Around 83 AG, the wolf spirit was spotted while drinking from a stream by Ikem, who had turned to a life of isolation in the forest near a river."
    },
    {
      "body": "Eighteen years later, when ${link_0} was traveling to ${link_1} in search of information about ${link_2}, ${link_3} began feeling a strange urge to constrict his face and sensed the presence of the wolf spirit. He briefly saw the wolf spirit a short while after, before being distracted by ${link_4}'s quick desertion. The wolf spirit appeared again and attempted to gnaw off Sokka's head. When Aang tried to respectfully approach the spirit and reveal his position as the ${link_5}, the wolf spirit quickly attacked him instead. Team Avatar tried multiple ways of attacking the spirit, all to no avail, until ${link_6} swiped the wolf spirit with his tail. He retaliated by throwing up a cloud of ${link_7}, which quickly surrounded Team Avatar. The spirit was eventually scared off by Azula's ${link_8} that struck the moths.",
